# Monetization & Subscription Standards

- Always design with subscription in mind: Free tier (limited), Pro ($9–$29/mo), optional Enterprise.
- Use Stripe: Checkout sessions, webhooks (create/update/cancel), customer portal.
- Protect features: Middleware / server actions မှာ subscription status check (Supabase + Stripe customer ID).
- Tiers features: Clearly define in code comments / docs.
- Free trial: 7–14 days auto.
- Analytics: Add simple event tracking (PostHog / Plausible snippet).